summary: This document consists of multiple photo sheet forms from the Metropolitan Correctional Center in New York, documenting a 'Possible Suicide Attempt' involving inmate Jeffrey Epstein on July 23, 2019, at 1:27 AM in the Special Housing Unit. The forms were prepared by a Lieutenant in the Special Investigative Section.
